author: Lisa Marks, Peter Fisher Real Estate
title: Lisa Marks, Peter Fisher Real Estate
text: From start to finish James Park was great to deal with - he was quick to respond to our questions and was very helpful. I would happily recommend Flashbay as a company worth dealing with as they have provided a quality product quickly and efficiently. Thank you!
